Bismillahirhemaanniraheem

◼
Zamana kyu na ho Ab gamgusaar Zehra ka

Shikasta pehlu huwa dil fegaar zahra ka
◼
Asa ko thaam ke aathi hai farshe majlis par

Karo Aai Ahle Aza intezar zahra ka
◾
Jala ke karbobala me kabhi madeene me 

Adu ne loota hai ghar baar baar zahra ka
◼
Khudaya behejde jaldi imame mehdi ko

Rahega Dhoop me kab tak Mazaar Zehra ka
◼
Mazaare fatema mismaar karne walo suno

Tumhe na chodega parwardigaar Zahra ka
◼
Rasan Ali ke gale me Jo bandhi AADA ne 

Huwa ye dekh ke dil Ashqbaar Zahra ka
◼
Sitam wo dhaaye rasoole Khuda ki Ummat ne 

Zamana aaj bhi hai sogwaar Zahra s.a ka
◼
Sitamgaro'n ke hai khabze me aaj bhi"Sibtain"

Hai kitna dekhiye bekas mazaar zahra ka
◼

✒️Sibtain sayyadi
